{"tid":1416294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知自己可以做咩既手足可唔可以一齊入黎","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:51:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:01:23.000Z","uid":260531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"41e2e57954658947fdc42e323b598159853cdaf4","tid":1416294,"uid":260531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:51:23.000Z","msg":"呢幾日發生咗好多事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />辛苦晒所有手足<br />\n好心痛阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日見林奠個鳩up記者會 <br />\n真係嬲到仆街 但係都唔可以絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢大概係想將我地既口號<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 =港獨<br />\n我地所有手足=港獨份子<br />\n等民鬥民<br />\n<br />\n先唔講我地係唔係想港獨先 <br />\n但係五大訴求一個都未成功 <br />\n係唔係要先搞掂咗先再提港獨呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dswy3Sw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDswy3Sw.png&h=cc3b0c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文宣既手足會唔會可以做文宣 令大家明白<br />\n呢句口號唔等於港獨 <br />\n而要唔要港獨就等五大訴求都成功咗之後先再討論<br />\n<br />\n同埋可唔可以文宣埋俾自己手足 <br />\n要搞搞黨旗 搞雜種<br />\n搞黨旗會唔會更對準政權呢<br />\n因為我問咗好多老一輩既人佢地7成都係大中華膠 <br />\n對中國莫名其妙地有好大既歸屬感 <br />\n但係同佢地講到到黨旗就馬上無所謂<br />\n好似天琦咁講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。</span></span><br />\n唔知咁會唔會可以更將革命既種子帶上去呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有諗過對大陸翻牆既人講 <br />\n你有能力翻牆點解唔去了解更多而係繼續睇翻大陸既新聞 <br />\n我見之前帝吧出精個時起底既都係一啲有咗覺悟既內地人做既<br />\n佢地都翻牆囉 點解唔去增加呢啲人既數量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望可以connect 到更多既人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人可能覺得民意唔係最重要 但係勇武手足付出咗好多 我地上街之外都有野可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得民意有好過無<br />\n大家可唔可以一齊黎俾更多意見 <br />\n睇下點可以令更多人支持我地<br />\n<br />\n我係P牌但係唔好因人廢言好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b801d128609328bd70cc93028e349e061c9c07a","tid":1416294,"uid":260531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:51:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8317ee701ff5a60b7f141b9c23c046d37ec7b492","tid":1416294,"uid":260531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:51:59.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"3e5c4f2b1d7180a1d05e24a6cd288ae658362456","tid":1416294,"uid":260531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:52:09.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"6354ddacc8b72dceb0d8c9c9321185db815257f9","tid":1416294,"uid":260531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:52:19.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"ddfee20691680e5d53810771803680c4a788475b","tid":1416294,"uid":260531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:52:30.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"fc10a4f417b0fe95b064390408fe80d76f5e8ff1","tid":1416294,"uid":260531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:52:40.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"1116a9af49499b7a50056297ec4db3037e7820fc","tid":1416294,"uid":260531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:52:53.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"8a475ffcecdf49664f7f82464bc567786b6cbd2c","tid":1416294,"uid":260531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:53:05.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"df5f541c65cada3733bab815439d834e0198b573","tid":1416294,"uid":260531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:53:15.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"f3550ecc2e20003ac81edee5d55adc0ec1a9de85","tid":1416294,"uid":260531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:53:37.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"9a25247b8a2aa1c0a30a698a3991c0a23d62fed9","tid":1416294,"uid":260531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:53:49.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"da44910f562bc50b27402cbbe5f8ca7baedafeab","tid":1416294,"uid":260531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:54:46.000Z","msg":"如果有人幫手推就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/f